{"tid":831143,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"居港外國籍巴絲，點解留喺香港？","createTime":"2018-09-21T16:35:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T10:30:14.000Z","uid":190818,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1343d8e59444ea469d15c2a651b37aff6bf57638","tid":831143,"uid":190818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T16:35:11.000Z","msg":"最近會諗自己留喺香港做乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人工唔係高<br />\n死慳死抵儲舊錢番黎，朋友覺得你好有錢<br />\n實情係中原指數新界東過撚埋200啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n舊首期儲儲下又加左一個double<br />\n為左間又貴又細最重要係買唔起嘅垃圾樓去捱<br />\n點撚解唔即刻劈炮去外國搏一搏呢？<br />\n去到外國無乜機會發大達<br />\n唔怕避苦做個藍領<br />\n起碼過到啲想過嘅生活，住大屋渣下車撚下狗<br />\n空氣都清新啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解我仲未的起心肝走<br />\n睇唔撚透"},{"pid":"a434f7656ab1af6b84135e561f956aef0260aa26","tid":831143,"uid":190818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T16:48:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/fight_connect_AB.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b4f87a2ebc40675cc71f9c90e9dd84212c1b30","tid":831143,"uid":118502,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T17:12:50.000Z","msg":"走唔出comfort zone"},{"pid":"86df2e4bdd80b95e61e240ba26e0272e58844765","tid":831143,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T22:51:38.000Z","msg":"easypussy"},{"pid":"a709cf210d4633d2b1841fa3df47ba01fe9a4ecd","tid":831143,"uid":190818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86df2e4bdd80b95e61e240ba26e0272e58844765","tid":831143,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T22:51:38.000Z","msg":"easypussy"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T23:20:41.000Z","msg":"巴打外國血統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"851e523a76f7210bad09